snippet: A fully restored, five-story townhouse on a prime tree-lined block on the Upper West Side was the sale of the week.
abstract: Big Ticket column; fully-renovated five-story townhouse near Central Park at West 87th Street on Upper West Side is highest residential sale of week in New York City, closing at $16,250,000.
lead_paragraph: A fully restored, five-story townhouse on a prime tree-lined block on the Upper West Side was the sale of the week.

headline.main: A Profitable Flip on the Upper West Side
